# bpkg
> Lightweight bash package manager

# Up and running
```bash
curl -Lo- "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/bpkg/bpkg/master/setup.sh" | bash
```

# Local or global installation of packges
```bash
bpkg install term  # locally installed from github.com/bpkg/term into ~/deps
bpkg install -g term  # globally installed from github.com/bpkg/term into /usr/local/bin
```

# Specify a version
```bash
bpkg install jwerle/suggest.sh@0.0.1 -g  # globally install from github.com/jwerle/suggest.sh
```
